      <title>蒙古旨在将中国煤炭销售提高到1亿吨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/mongolia-aims-to-boost-chinese-coal-sales-to-100-million-tons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蒙古的目标是今年将其对中国的煤炭出口近五分之一，因为它试图扩大与渴望资源的邻居的能源合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/mongolia-aims-to-boost-chinese-coal-sales-to-100-million-tons</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 09:25:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲人从马克龙的迷你穆斯特货物中排除了团结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/europeans-excluded-from-macron-s-mini-summit-fret-over-unity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几位欧盟领导人说，决定从巴黎匆忙安排的峰会中省略大多数成员国的决定，这发出了关于集团团结的错误信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/europeans-excluded-from-macron-s-mini-summit-fret-over-unity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 09:20:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯将在叙利亚后阿萨德后减少军事存在</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/russia-set-to-keep-reduced-military-presence-in-post-assad-syria</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们说，俄罗斯可能会减少在叙利亚的军事存在，这是弗拉基米尔·普京在阿萨德政权倒台之后的主要目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/russia-set-to-keep-reduced-military-presence-in-post-assad-syria</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 08:45:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的“黑匣子”关税配方在亚洲增加了不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/trump-s-broader-tariffs-would-pose-risk-to-asia-nomura-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据Nomura Holdings Inc.的经济学家称，唐纳德·特朗普总统上周对互惠关税的更广泛的定义可能会使我们的大多数亚洲经济体暴露给我们的税款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/trump-s-broader-tariffs-would-pose-risk-to-asia-nomura-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 08:19:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>立陶宛说，欧洲必须迅速加强国防支出。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/europe-must-rapidly-step-up-defense-spending-lithuania-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立陶宛国防部长Dovile Sakaliene说，欧洲需要迅速增加国防支出，以解决俄罗斯在乌克兰的入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/europe-must-rapidly-step-up-defense-spending-lithuania-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 08:05:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本允许台湾在家庭记录中列出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/japan-to-allow-taiwan-to-be-listed-in-family-records</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本将修改其规则，以允许台湾被列为其家庭注册处的原产地，此举将使人们与中国和台湾人的人民区分开来，这是北京宣称自己是自己的自治岛屿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/japan-to-allow-taiwan-to-be-listed-in-family-records</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 06:36:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸释放了1,000名骗局中心工人，因为镇压扩大了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/myanmar-rescues-1-000-scam-center-workers-as-crackdown-widens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸军政府表示，随着当局发誓要加强对跨国犯罪集团的镇压，已准备好将约1000名外国国民从泰国边境附近的网络骗局中心救出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-17/myanmar-rescues-1-000-scam-center-workers-as-crackdown-widens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Feb 2025 06:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国竞选活动与遗产候选人辩论有关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/german-campaign-sparks-into-life-with-testy-candidates-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的大选竞选活动周日爆发了生活，当时四个主要候选人在直播电视上发生冲突，在投票的主题投票之前，一周就交换了倒钩，从不规则移民到乌克兰的战争和该国的经济困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/german-campaign-sparks-into-life-with-testy-candidates-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 21:54:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡反对派领导人被定罪为民意调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/singapore-opposition-leader-faces-court-verdict-in-lying-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡的反对派领导人被法院因说谎的指控而被定罪和罚款，这一裁决可能会使他失去今年的民族大选的参赛资格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/singapore-opposition-leader-faces-court-verdict-in-lying-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟在普京的压力下寻求军事复兴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/eu-seeks-a-military-revival-under-pressure-from-putin-and-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统推动在乌克兰的战争迅速结束时，欧洲官员正在努力提高国防支出并支持基辅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/eu-seeks-a-military-revival-under-pressure-from-putin-and-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 15:59:06 GMT</pubDate>
